## ‚ú® Features

- [x] ü§ñ **AI-Powered Commit Messages**: Automatically generates high-quality commit messages using advanced language models, saving time and improving consistency;
- [x] üöÄ **One-Click Repository Management**: Simplifies repository tasks like generating descriptions, READMEs, and topics with a single command;
- [x] üìù **Customizable Prompts**: Offers flexible and customizable prompts for generating commit messages, descriptions, and topics tailored to your repository;
- [x] üîó **GitHub Integration**: Seamlessly integrates with GitHub to update repository descriptions and topics directly from the CLI;
- [x] üõ†Ô∏è **Extensible Architecture**: Built with a modular design, allowing for easy extension and customization of functionality;
- [x] üìä **Real-Time Feedback**: Provides live, real-time feedback during the generation process, ensuring accuracy and relevance;
- [x] üß† **Context-Aware Generation**: Analyzes repository content and context to produce highly relevant and accurate outputs;
- [x] üé® **Rich CLI Experience**: Features a visually appealing and user-friendly CLI interface powered by Rich, enhancing the user experience.

